<p><i><b>Blink: The Power of Thinking Without Thinking</b></i> is a <a href="/wiki/2005" title="2005">2005</a> book by <a href="/wiki/Malcolm_Gladwell" title="Malcolm Gladwell">Malcolm Gladwell</a>, in which he explores the power of the trained mind to make split second decisions.</p>
